title: La grande bellezza
overview: Jep Gambardella has seduced his way through the lavish nightlife of Rome for decades, but after his 65th birthday and a shock from the past, Jep looks past the nightclubs and parties to find a timeless landscape of absurd, exquisite beauty.

title: Jungfrukällan
overview: An innocent yet pampered young virgin and her family's pregnant and jealous servant set out to deliver candles to church, but only one returns from events that transpire in the woods along the way.

title: Mysterious Skin
overview: A teenage hustler and a young man obsessed with alien abductions cross paths, together discovering a horrible, liberating truth.

title: Network
overview: A television network cynically exploits a deranged former anchor's ravings and revelations about the news media for its own profit.

title: Jagten
overview: A teacher lives a lonely life, all the while struggling over his son's custody. His life slowly gets better as he finds love and receives good news from his son, but his new luck is about to be brutally shattered by an innocent little lie.

title: Midnight Cowboy
overview: A naive hustler travels from Texas to New York City to seek personal fortune, finding a new friend in the process.

title: Vivre sa vie: Film en douze tableaux
overview: Twelve episodic tales in the life of a Parisian woman and her slow descent into prostitution.

title: The Visitor
overview: A college professor travels to New York City to attend a conference and finds a young couple living in his apartment.

title: Kis Uykusu
overview: A hotel owner and landlord in a remote Turkish village deals with conflicts within his family and a tenant behind on his rent.

title: Mommy
overview: A widowed single mother, raising her violent son alone, finds new hope when a mysterious neighbor inserts herself into their household.

title: Black
overview: The cathartic tale of a young woman who can't see, hear or talk and the teacher who brings a ray of light into her dark world.

title: Il conformista
overview: A weak-willed Italian man becomes a fascist flunky who goes abroad to arrange the assassination of his old teacher, now a political dissident.

title: The Shawshank Redemption
overview: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

title: Le notti di Cabiria
overview: A waifish prostitute wanders the streets of Rome looking for true love but finds only heartbreak.

title: Todo sobre mi madre
overview: Young Esteban wants to become a writer and also to discover the identity of his second mother, a trans woman, carefully concealed by his mother Manuela.

title: Rain Man
overview: Selfish yuppie Charlie Babbitt's father left a fortune to his savant brother Raymond and a pittance to Charlie; they travel cross-country.

title: Magnolia
overview: An epic mosaic of interrelated characters in search of love, forgiveness, and meaning in the San Fernando Valley.

title: The Notebook
overview: A poor yet passionate young man falls in love with a rich young woman, giving her a sense of freedom, but they are soon separated because of their social differences.

title: Fa yeung nin wah
overview: Two neighbors, a woman and a man, form a strong bond after both suspect extramarital activities of their spouses. However, they agree to keep their bond platonic so as not to commit similar wrongs.
stars: ['Tony Chiu-Wai Leung', 'Maggie Cheung', 'Ping Lam Siu', "Tung Cho 'Joe' Cheung"]

title: Kramer vs. Kramer
overview: Ted Kramer's wife leaves him, allowing for a lost bond to be rediscovered between Ted and his son, Billy. But a heated custody battle ensues over the divorced couple's son, deepening the wounds left by the separation.
